{"tid":418371,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"求婚呢兩個字根本係侮辱緊男人","createTime":"2017-09-29T13:30:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-13T01:38:21.000Z","uid":144739,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5292c996bd74026b7aa7d231ce377204df1a0e80","tid":418371,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:30:11.000Z","msg":"一個男人如果希望你嘅伴侶同你結婚，根本唔應該用個「求 」字，而係用個「請 」字，姐係應該叫做請婚啊。<br />\n<br />\n另外男人係請婚嘅時候，更加唔應該響女人跪低，因為自古以來從來只有弱者向強者跪低，即係例如只有你屋企隻狗跪你，而你唔會跪番你屋企隻狗。<br />\n <br />\n所以最後希望大家會有所領悟，唔好有人唔做要做隻狗，用一個弱者身份去求你嘅伴侶答應你俾你坐監。"},{"pid":"713cb9f91ec7a203ea3066b1ad19160fa039ad64","tid":418371,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:32:58.000Z","msg":"我處女屠夫講嘅，以後邊個男人再講求婚呢兩個字，後代世世代代都冇處女屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ffe7880b2312bbb925fcfcf0f77916f9ce2bc49","tid":418371,"uid":104256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:35:22.000Z","msg":"求婚"},{"pid":"d0d807a195d00af5547fc8a530be5a540f6bd837","tid":418371,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:36:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>求婚</blockquote><br />\n祝你一世比狗屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeb46a3dd27ec14baa9b21424b2289db59bc6d36","tid":418371,"uid":10726,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:41:55.000Z","msg":"樓主應該係毒撚單身一個,<br />\n<br />\n你有機會同人求婚先上來發嗡風ok?"},{"pid":"2c760fd2140d7b23725a2d14fb0b0a2535157cd0","tid":418371,"uid":144739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T13:46:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主應該係毒撚單身一個,<br />\n<br />\n你有機會同人求婚先上來發嗡風ok?</blockquote><br />\nSorry就係屌女無數先有呢個領悟"},{"pid":"e0e45fd5cb16f5fa504a5e82ec7b52b24201cc97","tid":418371,"uid":28469,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T01:37:15.000Z","msg":"巴打你係咪hk_master<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e21d